52
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:07,500
Ustvari, mnogo komplikovanije.

53
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:10,833
Novca je više nego ikada.

54
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,666
Naš novac ima više
imena nego ikada pre.

55
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:18,166
Roba, zajmovi, akcije i obveznice.

56
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:21,000
Fondovi i fondovi fondova.

57
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:24,666
Budućnost, vrednost akcija,
derivati, konvertovani dug,

58
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,208
