424
00:26:37,125 --> 00:26:38,125
Prevara.

425
00:26:41,208 --> 00:26:43,166
Sve loše što sam uradio
bio je pokušaj uštede novca.

426
00:26:46,041 --> 00:26:48,500
Pokušao sam platiti manje
