457
00:28:45,333 --> 00:28:48,958
Tražim Glavnu ulicu br. 556.

458
00:28:49,333 --> 00:28:51,291
Da? Tamo je pošta.

459
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:54,833
Ne, ja tražim
Junajted Reosiguravajuću Grupu,

460
00:28:55,375 --> 00:28:57,625
koja je u Glavnoj ulici br. 556.

461
00:28:58,833 --> 00:29:00,625
Jumajted, kažete?
- Da.

462
00:29:00,833 --> 00:29:02,416
Ja... ja... ja... mislim...

463
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:05,000
mislim da ste pogrešno
zapisali adresu.

464
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:07,833
Ne, ne, pogledala sam.
To je Junajted Reosiguranje.

465
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:12,333
Oni reosiguravaju prijatna krstarenja,
sigurna sam i druge stvari, ali...

466
00:29:12,541 --> 00:29:16,291
zapravo tražim čoveka po imenu
Bonka... Bonkamper.

467
00:29:19,458 --> 00:29:21,125
Ne poznajem ga.

468
00:29:36,333 --> 00:29:37,541
Tata!

469
00:29:44,625 --> 00:29:45,708
G. Bonkamper?

470
00:29:47,458 --> 00:29:48,458
Da.

471
00:29:48,708 --> 00:29:51,833
Direktor Junajted Reosiguravajuće
Grupe Nivesa?

472
00:29:58,083 --> 00:30:01,166
O Bože, pripazi na sestre.
Izvinite!

473
00:30:02,375 --> 00:30:03,625
Gospoðo. Izvinite gospoðo.

474
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:06,625
Možete li se udaljiti?
- Ja sam mu žena. Ostavite me.

475
00:30:07,208 --> 00:30:09,625
Irvine. 
- Vinsel Bonkamper?

476
00:30:09,708 --> 00:30:10,708
Edit.

477
00:30:11,166 --> 00:30:14,333
Ko je doðavola Vinsel?
Vi ljudi čak ni ne znate ko je on.

478
00:30:14,791 --> 00:30:15,791
Irvine?

479
00:30:17,916 --> 00:30:19,333
Da. Edit?

480
00:30:21,666 --> 00:30:23,833
Možemo li razgovarati
nasamo na trenutak?

481
00:30:35,666 --> 00:30:39,000
Ova žena, to je Vinsel Bonkamper.

482
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:41,916
Druga žena vašeg muža.
- Šta?

483
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:45,333
G. Bonkamper ima drugu porodicu.
Oni žive u Nivesu.

484
00:30:46,583 --> 00:30:47,958
Ti pizdurino!

485
00:30:48,208 --> 00:30:51,166
Sklanjate ruke s mene!
Mrtav si! Mrtav si!

486
00:30:51,583 --> 00:30:52,750
Daj mi moju decu.

487
00:30:54,250 --> 00:30:56,458
Vodimo ga odavde. Idemo.
- Draga?

